name: Otet de mere nefiltrat bio
description:
Ingredients:
Unfiltered apple cider vinegar, 5% acidity. Comes from organic farming.
Dennree organic apple cider vinegar from wine offers pure joy. The vinegar is easily obtained from aromatic organic apples, natural juices, whose natural juice is fermented, transformed into wine, then into vinegar. It gives salads, raw vegetables and many dishes a touch of refinement. Diluted with water or juice, it is an ideal refreshing drink. Enjoy the taste of fruit and acidity.
It will be shaken before consumption.

description:

suc de varza acra* fermentat cu acid lactic (99%), sare de mare (0,9%), antioxidant: acid ascorbic. *provin din agricultura ecologica.
